{"tid":2290990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM女練習生HELEN在韓網引發討論！網友：「很適合aespa的感覺，以後會加入嗎？」","createTime":"2020-11-18T12:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T15:23:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22de85963762a49dda11203acbf5b6841ee55d45","tid":2290990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b7434f5d4ae30d20082eb4e28411fe9d/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-18/131728-885328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b7434f5d4ae30d20082eb4e28411fe9d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-18%2F131728-885328.jpg&h=de9df27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前一直有在傳aespa會是7人組，不知道之後是否會真的加成員呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSM娛樂時隔6年推出新女團aespa，由KARINA、GISELLE、WINTER、NINGNING 4位成員組成。昨日（17日）帶著單曲《Black Mamba》正式出道，不知道大家有沒有聽過她們的歌呢？<br />\n<br />\n近日，SM有位女練習生也在網路上引發討論，這位練習生叫做Helen（헬렌），2003年出生，澳洲僑胞。雖然是未公開練習生，但在學院中告知進了SM因而被知曉。網友們也表示：「好可愛... 希望能出道」、「照片怎麼看起來都長不太一樣」、「感覺很適合aespa」、「看來這位以後會加入」、「怎麼感覺跟GISELLE有點像」、「會加入到追加成員當中嗎」等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1a774b51b6a4c7a190920eb4ad9fc6b1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-18/131728-885322.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1a774b51b6a4c7a190920eb4ad9fc6b1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-18%2F131728-885322.png&h=c5e56563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_134f6ef99dde70916f40123e3254a4de/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-18/131728-885323.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_134f6ef99dde70916f40123e3254a4de%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-18%2F131728-885323.png&h=c59d8d75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f8198914e82a340249ae4e5d3dc21a62/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-18/131728-885324.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f8198914e82a340249ae4e5d3dc21a62%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-18%2F131728-885324.png&h=9cfa1e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，有位自稱是相關人士的人在推特透露過aespa會是「4+3」體制，其中+3裡有一位的名字縮寫就是海倫。而Red Velvet也是4人組出道，隔年加入新成員Yeri，新女團aespa之後是否會再加入新成員，也引發關注。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a9ca3242a62a4abafe9cd85585f5b3ad/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-18/131728-885326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a9ca3242a62a4abafe9cd85585f5b3ad%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-18%2F131728-885326.jpg&h=ad523ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖：Youtube@SMTOWN、Theqoo）"},{"pid":"88d122ec9555ee01d24fca9479f3cd14e27af767","tid":2290990,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"都唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542129463a57b10abc69d5318b995938fe5c8ea0","tid":2290990,"uid":256796,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P16ZOYQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP16ZOYQ.gif&h=884184bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e7914b9fe08b3c730bfe3c7ce473c72c9a7358a","tid":2290990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88d122ec9555ee01d24fca9479f3cd14e27af767","tid":2290990,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"都唔錯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"Welcome<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8976718edc232d946b76d